snippet: Andy Murray’s hometown, Dunblane, Scotland, bubbled over with excitement during the Wimbledon final, despite the end result.
abstract: Crowds of people pack into pubs and social halls in, Dunblane, Scotland, hometown of tennis star Andy Murray, to watch him compete in the Wimbledon final against Roger Federer.
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray’s hometown, Dunblane, Scotland, bubbled over with excitement during the Wimbledon final, despite the end result.

headline.seo: Scottish Town Rises And Falls With Andy Murray
